Out of Sync 

"You haven't changed through the years," 

I am often enviously told. 

But the secret of my achievement 

Is that when young, I looked old. 

-- Mimi Kay. 

Workplace Wisdom 

Corporate committee meetings and professional football games have a lot in common: The participants are well paid, highly motivated, very competitive -- and every time one of them grabs the ball and tries to run with it, 11 other people jump on top of him. 

-- Robert Orben. 

Candid Comment 

Gossips and vacuum cleaners both pick up dirt.
The difference is that it stays inside a vacuum cleaner] 

-- Frank Walsh. 

